I'm the one who set up the barrier, though.

It's not just something, the succubus village is

That's why it's troublesome that they immediately

Well, the main reason is that the leader of the

diminished.

It seems that they have asked the guild's magical

I see... I should meet this Louisa once and hear

I'm willing to lend a hand.

to the southwest from here.

I've set up a mechanism to prevent you from making

I see, it would be troublesome if the enemy used

Ah, I see. Well, as long as you're recognized by

Be careful because there are many enemies in the

Thank you for everything, Dark and Aldo.

I'm counting on you.
